               <msContents>
                  <summary>The codex includes the Pauline Epistles, Acts, Revelation, and the
                     Apostolic Epistles. Modern paper fly-leaves were added at the beginning and end
                     of the codex. The codex is probably comprised of four manuscripts of different
                     dates bound together. </summary>
