                     <handNote script="Ethiopic" xml:id="h1">
                        <seg type="script">
                           Written in black ink. There seem to be four or five different hands: ff.
                           3-20, a poor hand, small and square; ff. 21-76, a very fair hand of an
                           earlier type, tall and clear; ff. 77-110, a thick clumsy hand; ff.
                           111-123, small and neat; ff. 124-140, similar to preceding hand but less neat. 
                        </seg>
                     </handNote>
